Gauteng Education MEC Panyaza Lesufi. Twitter/Panyaza Lesufi JOHANNESBURG - Gauteng Education MEC Panyaza Lesufi will visit the Edenglen High School in Ekurhuleni on Wednesday. This after footage emerged of pupils fighting outside the school premises. In the video that went viral on social media, pupils are seen fiercely brawling. READ: School violence a reflection of society: expert It's unclear what led to the fight. In a statement, Lesufi said violence will not be tolerated.